    <item>
      <title>美国拆除加沙码头且无恢复前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/us-dismantles-gaza-pier-with-no-prospect-of-bringing-it-back</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼拆除了向加沙地带运送援助物资的临时码头，并且目前没有恢复该码头的计划，这对该计划造成了又一次打击，该计划已成为美国缓解加沙地带严重人道主义危机的象征。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/us-dismantles-gaza-pier-with-no-prospect-of-bringing-it-back</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 18:57:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
